headline: Morgan Stanley Lifts Smurfit Westrock (SW) PT to 4,000GBp on 2026 Synergy Gains
summary: Smurfit Westrock (NYSE:SW) is one of the cheap stocks to buy for the next 3 years. On January 8, Morgan Stanley raised the firm’s price target on Smurfit Westrock to 4,000 GBp from 3,900 GBp, while maintaining an Overweight rating on the shares.
